% Demo purpose: create a compact structured payload for optional AI explanation.
% Expected findings: SG004 ERROR, SG007 INFO, and SG014 INFO.
% Geometry settings: not required; use purpose shown in examples/demo/README.md.
% Scope: independently written, simplified, and not a production reactor model.

surf known_boundary cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40

cell review_cell 0 fuel -known_boundary missing_boundary

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -1.0

mat reserved_material -1.0
1001.09c -1.0

set bc 2
